      ānayasva pitaraṃ saṃśitavrataṃ; gāṃdhārīṃ ca mahiṣīm ājamīḍha  
  7 tau te 'suyāṃ vinayetāṃ narendra; dharmajñau tau nipuṇau
niścayajñau  
