      abhyupetya mahāprājñaḥ kṛṣṇadvaipāyano 'bravīt  
  9 saṃpṛcchate dhṛtarāṣṭrāya saṃjaya; ācakṣva sarvaṃ yāvad eṣo
'nuyuṅkte  
